sql:
SELECT course_name, cost_usd
FROM courses
WHERE cost_usd = (SELECT MAX(cost_usd) FROM courses);

external_knowledge:
- "captains steering the ships of knowledge" refers to instructors teaching courses;
- "tranquil waters of the Regular track" refers to courses that belong to the Regular track as defined by the tracks table;
- "collective treasure" refers to the total cost in USD of the courses taught by each instructor.
